  "instructions": [
    "in a small bowl, whisk together agave nectar, dashi extract, lemon juice, and orange juice until well combined.",
    "in a separate bowl, mix together pineapple chunks and ginger syrup (if using).",
    "arrange the pineapple chunks in the center of the agave leaf, spooning some of the citrus mixture over the top.",
    "sprinkle a pinch of kosher salt over the pineapple and garnish with sliced almonds and fresh mint leaves.",
    "place the agave leaf on a serving plate and garnish with additional mint leaves, if desired."
